---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import { Badge } from '@/components/ui/badge';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Unleft handles your data.">
  <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 px-4">
      <Badge className="mb-6 bg-accent-primary/10 text-accent-glow border-none mx-auto w-fit">Legal & Safety</Badge>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-text-primary mb-8 tracking-tighter" style={{ fontFamily: "'Bruno Ace SC', sans-serif" }}>
        Privacy <span class="text-accent-primary">Policy</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-secondary leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Transparency is at our core. Here is how we handle your data with precision and care.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-8 text-sm font-mono text-accent-glow uppercase tracking-widest">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-accent-primary/5 rounded-3xl blur-3xl opacity-50"></div>
      <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-[#2D2D44] bg-[#0A0A0F]/60 p-8 md:p-12 backdrop-blur-sm shadow-2xl">
        <div class="prose prose-invert prose-headings:font-heading prose-headings:text-text-primary prose-p:text-text-secondary prose-li:text-text-secondary prose-a:text-accent-glow max-w-none prose-h2:text-2xl prose-h2:mt-12 prose-h2:mb-6">
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p>We collect information you provide directly when using our contact form: your name, email address, company name (optional), and message content. We do not collect sensitive personal data.</p>
      
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>To respond to your inquiries and project requests</li>
            <li>To improve our services</li>
            <li>To send follow-up communications (only if consent is given)</li>
          </ul>
      
          <h2>3. Data Storage & Security</h2>
          <p>Form submissions are processed through Vercel Edge Functions and delivered via Resend email service. We do not maintain a database of user submissions beyond email records. All data transmission is encrypted via TLS.</p>
      
          <h2>4. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Vercel</strong> — Hosting and serverless functions</li>
            <li><strong>Resend</strong> — Email delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Google reCAPTCHA</strong> — Spam protection (subject to Google's privacy policy)</li>
            <li><strong>Google Fonts</strong> — Typography (loaded from Google CDN)</li>
          </ul>
      
          <h2>5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies for site functionality and consent management. Analytics cookies are only used with your explicit consent. See our <a href="/legal/cookies">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</p>
      
          <h2>6. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to request access, correction, or deletion of any personal data we hold. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@Unleft.space">hello@Unleft.space</a>.</p>
      
          <h2>7. Contact</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related inquiries: <a href="mailto:hello@Unleft.space">hello@Unleft.space</a></p>
          <p>Location: Dhaka, Bangladesh</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>
